{
  "texts": [
    "Further research in local languages and dialects could be useful but was outside the scope of this project.",
    "The researchers relied on their own language capabilities in Arabic, English, French, and Spanish, and used DeepL for other translations.In addition, the researchers selected specific country-based publications on LexisNexis to control for the source of the originating information.",
    "However, LexisNexis does not provide equal country coverage and can sometimes return too much noise because of its end of article country name \"tags.\"",
    "Therefore, LexisNexis data collection was supplemented by GoogleAdvanced search as well as other reference sites, which were utilized following core research (LexisNexis and Google Advanced search).",
    "For a list of the 15 additional reference sites see the next section.Further, the focus on national, competitive elections excludes regional elections, as well as, for example, elections for the European Parliament."
  ]
}